   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Project 100 — Local AI Ops Mini-Platform (Capstone)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"## The Grand Finale: Chat + RAG + Tools + Evals — All Combined\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**What you'll learn:**\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Integrate conversational AI, RAG, tool use, structured output, evaluation, and observability into one local platform\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Combine techniques from all 99 previous projects into a unified architecture\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Stack:** LangChain · LangGraph · Ollama · ChromaDB · Pydantic · Jupyter\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This capstone project combines techniques from all 99 previous projects into a single\\n\",\n",
    "    \"integrated platform: conversational AI, RAG retrieval, tool use, structured output,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"evaluation, and observability — all running locally.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# !pip install -q langchain langchain-ollama langchain-community chromadb pydantic\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 1 — Core LLM & Embeddings\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"from langchain_ollama import ChatOllama, OllamaEmbeddings\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.prompts import ChatPromptTemplate\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.documents import Document\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_community.vectorstores import Chroma\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from langchain_text_splitters import RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from pydantic import BaseModel, Field\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import json, time, shutil\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from pathlib import Path\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from datetime import datetime\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Core models\\n\",\n",
    "    \"llm = ChatOllama(model=\\\"qwen3:8b\\\", temperature=0.2)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"embeddings = OllamaEmbeddings(model=\\\"nomic-embed-text\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"✓ Module 1: Core LLM & Embeddings initialized\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 2 — Knowledge Base (RAG)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Build a knowledge base from the project's own documentation\\n\",\n",
    "    \"knowledge_docs = [\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    Document(page_content=\\\"LangChain is a framework for building LLM-powered applications. \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"It provides chains, agents, and retrieval components. Key abstractions include \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"ChatModels, Prompts, OutputParsers, and Retrievers.\\\", metadata={\\\"topic\\\": \\\"langchain\\\"}),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    Document(page_content=\\\"Ollama runs LLMs locally. Supported models include Llama 3, Qwen, \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"Mistral, Phi-3, and Gemma. It provides an OpenAI-compatible API at localhost:11434. \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"Models are pulled with 'ollama pull model_name'.\\\", metadata={\\\"topic\\\": \\\"ollama\\\"}),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    Document(page_content=\\\"ChromaDB is an open-source vector database for AI applications. \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"It stores embeddings and supports similarity search. It can run in-memory or \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"persistently. Key operations: add, query, delete.\\\", metadata={\\\"topic\\\": \\\"chromadb\\\"}),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    Document(page_content=\\\"LangGraph extends LangChain with stateful, multi-step workflows. \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"It uses StateGraph with typed state dictionaries. Nodes are functions, edges define \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"flow. Supports conditional routing and human-in-the-loop.\\\", metadata={\\\"topic\\\": \\\"langgraph\\\"}),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    Document(page_content=\\\"RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) combines search with generation. \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"Steps: 1) Index documents as embeddings, 2) Retrieve relevant chunks for a query, \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"3) Generate answers grounded in retrieved context.\\\", metadata={\\\"topic\\\": \\\"rag\\\"}),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    Document(page_content=\\\"CrewAI enables multi-agent collaboration. Define Agents with roles \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"and backstories, Tasks with descriptions, and Crews that orchestrate execution. \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"Supports sequential and hierarchical processes.\\\", metadata={\\\"topic\\\": \\\"crewai\\\"}),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"splitter = RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter(chunk_size=200, chunk_overlap=30)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"chunks = splitter.split_documents(knowledge_docs)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"shutil.rmtree(\\\"chroma_capstone\\\", ignore_errors=True)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"vectorstore = Chroma.from_documents(chunks, embeddings, persist_directory=\\\"chroma_capstone\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"retriever = vectorstore.as_retriever(search_kwargs={\\\"k\\\": 3})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"✓ Module 2: Knowledge base built — {len(chunks)} chunks indexed\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 3 — Tool Registry\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"from langchain_core.tools import tool\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"@tool\\n\",\n",
    "    \"def search_knowledge_base(query: str) -> str:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"\\\"\\\"Search the AI knowledge base for information.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    docs = retriever.invoke(query)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return \\\"\\\\n\\\".join([f\\\"[{d.metadata.get('topic','?')}] {d.page_content}\\\" for d in docs])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"@tool\\n\",\n",
    "    \"def analyze_code(code: str) -> str:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"\\\"\\\"Analyze Python code for issues and improvements.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    prompt = ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        (\\\"system\\\", \\\"Analyze this code briefly. List any bugs, security issues, or improvements.\\\"),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        (\\\"human\\\", \\\"{code}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    chain = prompt | llm | StrOutputParser()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return chain.invoke({\\\"code\\\": code})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"@tool\\n\",\n",
    "    \"def generate_summary(text: str) -> str:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"\\\"\\\"Summarize text into 3 key bullet points.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    prompt = ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        (\\\"system\\\", \\\"Summarize in exactly 3 bullet points.\\\"),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        (\\\"human\\\", \\\"{text}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    chain = prompt | llm | StrOutputParser()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return chain.invoke({\\\"text\\\": text})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"tools = [search_knowledge_base, analyze_code, generate_summary]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"✓ Module 3: {len(tools)} tools registered: {[t.name for t in tools]}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 4 — Evaluation Engine\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"class EvalResult(BaseModel):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    query: str\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    answer: str\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    groundedness: float = Field(ge=0, le=1)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    relevance: float = Field(ge=0, le=1)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    quality: float = Field(ge=0, le=1)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    latency_s: float\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"eval_judge = llm.with_structured_output(EvalResult)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"class TraceLog:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    def __init__(self):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        self.entries = []\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    def log(self, event, data, duration=0):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        self.entries.append({\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"timestamp\\\": datetime.now().isoformat(),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"event\\\": event,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"data_size\\\": len(str(data)),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"duration_s\\\": round(duration, 3),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        })\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    def summary(self):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        return {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"total_events\\\": len(self.entries),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"total_duration\\\": sum(e[\\\"duration_s\\\"] for e in self.entries),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"events\\\": [e[\\\"event\\\"] for e in self.entries],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        }\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"trace = TraceLog()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"✓ Module 4: Evaluation engine & trace logger ready\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 5 — Integrated Pipeline\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"def ai_ops_pipeline(query):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"\\\"\\\"Full pipeline: retrieve → generate → evaluate → trace.\\\"\\\"\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    results = {}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    # Step 1: Retrieve\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    start = time.time()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    context_docs = retriever.invoke(query)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    context = \\\"\\\\n\\\".join([d.page_content for d in context_docs])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    retrieve_time = time.time() - start\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    trace.log(\\\"retrieve\\\", context, retrieve_time)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    # Step 2: Generate\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    start = time.time()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    qa_prompt = ChatPromptTemplate.from_messages([\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        (\\\"system\\\", \\\"Answer based on the context. Be accurate and cite sources.\\\"),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        (\\\"human\\\", \\\"Context:\\\\n{context}\\\\n\\\\nQuestion: {query}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    chain = qa_prompt | llm | StrOutputParser()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    answer = chain.invoke({\\\"context\\\": context, \\\"query\\\": query})\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    generate_time = time.time() - start\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    trace.log(\\\"generate\\\", answer, generate_time)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    # Step 3: Evaluate\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    start = time.time()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    try:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        evaluation = eval_judge.invoke(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            f\\\"Evaluate this Q&A:\\\\nQuery: {query}\\\\nAnswer: {answer}\\\\n\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            f\\\"Context: {context[:300]}\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        )\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        eval_scores = {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"groundedness\\\": evaluation.groundedness,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"relevance\\\": evaluation.relevance,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"quality\\\": evaluation.quality,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        }\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    except Exception:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        eval_scores = {\\\"groundedness\\\": 0.5, \\\"relevance\\\": 0.5, \\\"quality\\\": 0.5}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    eval_time = time.time() - start\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    trace.log(\\\"evaluate\\\", eval_scores, eval_time)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"query\\\": query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"answer\\\": answer,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"sources\\\": [d.metadata.get(\\\"topic\\\") for d in context_docs],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"scores\\\": eval_scores,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        \\\"timing\\\": {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"retrieve\\\": round(retrieve_time, 2),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"generate\\\": round(generate_time, 2),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"evaluate\\\": round(eval_time, 2),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"total\\\": round(retrieve_time + generate_time + eval_time, 2),\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        },\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    }\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"✓ Module 5: Integrated pipeline ready\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 6 — Run the Platform\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"queries = [\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"What is RAG and how does it work?\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"How does LangGraph differ from LangChain?\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"What models can I run with Ollama?\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"Explain how ChromaDB stores embeddings\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"How do CrewAI agents collaborate?\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"all_results = []\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"LOCAL AI OPS PLATFORM — RUNNING\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"=\\\"*60)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for q in queries:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    result = ai_ops_pipeline(q)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    all_results.append(result)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"\\\\nQ: {result['query']}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"A: {result['answer'][:200]}...\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"Sources: {result['sources']}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"Scores: G={result['scores']['groundedness']:.0%} \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"          f\\\"R={result['scores']['relevance']:.0%} \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"          f\\\"Q={result['scores']['quality']:.0%}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"Timing: {result['timing']['total']:.1f}s \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"          f\\\"(retrieve={result['timing']['retrieve']:.1f} \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"          f\\\"generate={result['timing']['generate']:.1f} \\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"          f\\\"eval={result['timing']['evaluate']:.1f})\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Module 7 — Platform Dashboard\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import pandas as pd\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Performance summary\\n\",\n",
    "    \"metrics_df = pd.DataFrame([{\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"query\\\": r[\\\"query\\\"][:40],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"groundedness\\\": r[\\\"scores\\\"][\\\"groundedness\\\"],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"relevance\\\": r[\\\"scores\\\"][\\\"relevance\\\"],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"quality\\\": r[\\\"scores\\\"][\\\"quality\\\"],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"latency\\\": r[\\\"timing\\\"][\\\"total\\\"],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"} for r in all_results])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"\\\\n\\\" + \\\"=\\\"*60)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"PLATFORM DASHBOARD\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"=\\\"*60)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\nQueries processed: {len(all_results)}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\nQuality Metrics:\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  Avg Groundedness: {metrics_df['groundedness'].mean():.0%}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  Avg Relevance:    {metrics_df['relevance'].mean():.0%}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  Avg Quality:      {metrics_df['quality'].mean():.0%}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\nPerformance:\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  Avg Latency:  {metrics_df['latency'].mean():.1f}s\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  P95 Latency:  {metrics_df['latency'].quantile(0.95):.1f}s\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\nTrace Summary:\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"trace_summary = trace.summary()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  Total events: {trace_summary['total_events']}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"  Total time:   {trace_summary['total_duration']:.1f}s\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\nDetailed Results:\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(metrics_df.to_string(index=False))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"\\\\n{'='*60}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"🎉 CAPSTONE COMPLETE — All 100 Projects Finished!\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"=\\\"*60)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## Capstone Summary\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"This project combined ALL major techniques from the 100-project series:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Module | Technique | From Projects |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"|--------|-----------|---------------|\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Core LLM | Ollama + LangChain | 1-10 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Knowledge Base | ChromaDB + RAG | 11-30 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Tools | Tool registry + execution | 51-60 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Evaluation | LLM-as-judge + scoring | 61-70 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Observability | Trace logging + metrics | 61-70 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Structured Output | Pydantic models | Throughout |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Pipeline | End-to-end orchestration | 31-40 |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Congratulations on completing all 100 Local AI Projects!**\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  }\n",
    " ],\n",
